# Foundry build output + cache — regenerate via `forge build`.
# Under `artifacts/`, three formats are committed:
#
#   *.bin-runtime  — hex runtime bytecode with immutables patched.
#                    Used by `reth --dev` genesis alloc + `cast code`
#                    smoke tests.
#   *.bin          — raw-binary variant of .bin-runtime, consumed by
#                    `include_bytes!` in `crates/chainspec/`.
#   *.bin-creation — hex creation bytecode (constructor + runtime,
#                    immutables unpatched), pasted into op-node's
#                    upgrade-tx payload constants.
#
# All three are produced by `just contracts-eip8130-build`.
out/
cache/
